channel.title: Buried614 Reborn
channel.description:
Yes Buried614 has returned after a long time. A few days ago, [b]Marcus[/b](Former Owner) messaged me and asked if i'd be interested in helping him bring the server back. We've done quite a few bug fixes, and fixed a few pieces of content and are now ready to start our long journey once again.
[center][B]WARNING: YOU must have a forum account to login![/B] [COLOR=blue]Forums: [url=http://buried614.com]Click Here[/url] Jar Download: [url=http://buried614.com/Buried614.jar]Click Here[/url]
[spoiler=New Media][img]http://i.imgur.com/Maolc5L.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/h0uIhnU.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/e1pniQE.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/fev754T.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/PrAhuFl.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/He0dE90.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/kORfhr1.png[/img][/spoiler]
[spoiler=Old Media][img]http://i.imgur.com/em9a7XJ.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/ndCCXpN.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/JwaLXi3.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/iyJyDwg.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/FXRRQ7H.png[/img]
[/spoiler]
[center][u]Buried614 Features[/u]
- Bridding - Autocast (100%) - Fully equipped Pkshop - PkP System - Killstreak System - Decent and fun economy. - 24/7 Uptime - Vote4Cash - Vote4PkPoints - Trading - Webclient - 100% Private Messaging - Active helpful staff - 2 Levels of Donator status - Great updates! - Completely Lag Free! - 100% working leeches - Working Korasi’s Sword - Multi Barrages - Xp Counter - Working weapon specs and effects - Working curses prayer book, including turmoil! - All spell books, Moderns, Ancients and Lunars - All Spirit shields working, Even their affects. - Working Teleblock - Staff of light Special - Yell with custom tags - Bank Tabs[/center]
We hope to see you online :) If you have any questions/concerns, feel free to private myself or [b]Marcus[/b]
Regards,
Buried614 Administration Team
